Reduce File Size 


ls -lh : list detailed in human readable format

gzip filename : compress file
gunzip filename.gz : decompress file

 Preserve properties and Compress Folder {
    tar -cvf NewName.tar foldername : create tar archive as file format
    gzip NewName.tar : compress above tar 

    OR 

    tar -czvf NewName.tar.gz foldername
}

Decompress Folder {
 tar -xvf NewName.tar.gz : decompress Folder
}

zip NewName.zip file1 file2 : Compress multiple files
unzip NewName.zip : decompress above

tar -tczf filename.tar.gz : list in detail files or folders in zipped folder
zipinfo NewName.zip : Above Alternative

zcat ZippedFileName : read contents of zipeed file
